biography: The namesake brand of fashion icon #KARLLAGERFELD

latestIgtvVideos.caption: French countryside escapes. Senior Vice President of Image and Communications Caroline Lebar enjoys breaks from city in summer to unwind and recharge. She keeps an eye on the KARL family from afar to ensure a seamless transition into fall and the upcoming launch of the CARA LOVES KARL collection. Stay tuned!​ #TeamKARL​ #KARLLAGERFELD

Defined routines. As a sports enthusiast, Menswear Ambassador and Product Consultant Sébastien Jondeau appreciates structure and fun in equal measure, so he he tries to add a bit of excitement to everything he does, even in summer.​ #TeamKARL​ #KARLLAGERFELD

A movable feast. KARL LAGERFELD Design Director Hun Kim appreciates exquisite food and all the aesthetics that surround the artform. As a result, travel, beauty and culinary exploration go hand in hand. ​#TeamKARL​ #KARLLAGERFELD
Majestic splendor. Sustainability Ambassador Amber Valletta advocates spending mindful time in nature to refocus and appreciate the beauty of the world we live in #TeamKarl​ #KARLLAGERFELD

Summer reset. Make a style statement and indulge in the one-of-a-kind collaboration with the namesake brand of Archie Alled-Martinez. Unapologetic, bold, and exclusive, the collection celebrates Karl’s life through a queer lens and showcases elevated, gender-neutral pieces that pull the focus in any setting #KARLLAGERFELD #TeamKARL

Up close and personal. Have a look at the discussion between #KARLLAGERFELD Style Advisor Carine Roitfeld and designer Archie Alled-Martinez, to learn more about the exclusive, gender-neutral collection.

From concept to creation. Check out the making of the exclusive #KarlxEndless medallions that bridge the void between physical and digital
reality in the latest NFT adventure from #KARLLAGERFELD.
#KARLNFTCOLLECTION
@thedematerialised

Tantalizing in all the best ways. Discover the seductive holiday mood of the #KARLLAGERFELD beachwear collection. 

Credits to @artemispolemis @vinaneofotistou & @kaplanidis.
Vibrant summer uplift. Step into the brightness of the new collection from #KARLLAGERFELD.
Beach-ready elegance. Spanish singer-songwriter @evaruiz is the epitome of summer chic. #KARLLAGERFELD
Elevated urban-beach style. German actor @dennis.mojen stars in a string of shows as well as the new summer photo shoot from #KARLLAGERFELD.
Where the city meets the sea. French artist, rapper and #TEAMKARL member @sneazzysneazzy is the face of #KARLLAGERFELD underwear and is prominently featured in the latest summer campaign.

latestPosts.caption:
Premiering tonight: ‘KARL – The Man Behind the Mask’. The new documentary by Gero von Boehm explores the life and legacy of Karl Lagerfeld.
 
The first extract revisits Karl’s passion for sketching, followed by anecdotes from Caroline Lebar, SVP of Image and Communications at KARL LAGERFELD and long-time friend, and the story of Sébastien Jondeau, brand ambassador and Karl’s former bodyguard.
 
Tune in on @3sat at 8.15pm to watch the full documentary.
#KARLLAGERFELD

latestPosts.caption:
Seoul, thank you. Our pop-up in South Korea opened with the vibrant energy of friends of the House celebrating Karl Lagerfeld’s creative vision and legacy. 
A heartfelt thanks to everyone who made this moment possible. #KARLLAGERFELD

Curated under the direction of our Creative Director and of Seoul-native @hunkim_official, the KARL LAGERFELD pop-up arrives in South Korea for the very first time. Set in the heart of Seongsu, this immersive space pays tribute to Karl’s legacy — and to the city that shaped Hun’s own creative journey. It’s a celebration of fashion, storytelling, and connection.

Open from May 17th–26th.
#KARLLAGERFELD
